item.title: [HIVE-8201] Remove hardwiring to HiveInputFormat in acid qfile tests
item.description: Now that HIVE-7812 is checked in we should remove the hardwiring to HiveInputFormat for the qfile tests.
item.summary: Remove hardwiring to HiveInputFormat in acid qfile tests

status.description: The issue is considered finished, the resolution is correct. Issues which are not closed can be reopened.

comments.comment: Turns out this is more than just a testing issue. A small change was needed to OrcInputFormat to handle the case when an update or delete is being done to a table in non-acid format.
owen.omalley could you take a look at the changes to OrcInputFormat and make sure they look right?
